Received: (dci@localhost) by zarquon.uchicago.edu (8.6.9/8.6.5) id OAA07150 for gmeeker@volga.EECS.Berkeley.EDU; Tue, 13 Dec 1994 14:18:39 -0600
From: Dan Isaksen <dci@math.uchicago.edu>
Message-Id: <199412132018.OAA07150@zarquon.uchicago.edu>
Subject: Re: CalChart
To: gmeeker@pasteur.EECS.Berkeley.EDU (Garrick Meeker)
Date: Tue, 13 Dec 1994 14:18:38 -0600 (CST)
In-Reply-To: <Pine.3.89.9412122231.A10837-0100000@volga.EECS.Berkeley.EDU> from "Garrick Meeker" at Dec 12, 94 10:59:23 pm
