> Okay, I understand.  I think this could be a little clearer, however.  
> The modes should reflect the action executed by right clicks.  So you 
> have a smart move mode, 8 symbol modes, a label flip mode, etc.  For 
> more powerful actions, such as transformations, block actions, use some 
> sort of icons menus that are just simple selections; they don't change 
