Isn't it amazing how sometimes you get started on an idea, and you think
you are improving it, but really you are missing the truly clear solution
simply because you started in the wrong frame of mind.  You have certainly
greatly demistified the situation.  The point is this: my informal concept
of mode really meant an option to define rightclick to be what you want.

As for the specific comment about 8 symbol modes, I think it may be better
to base the symbolrelated commands on the concept of having a current
symbol, and then all commands will operate relative to THAT symbol.  This
is essentially the way that the current version works, but icons will make
choosing a new symbol much easier.

