> Nothing to be sorry about.  Because of your message I discover another 
> bug.  I just fixed it.  It will be on the web page shortly.  No need to 
> get it if $CALCHART_RT is set, however.  Under Windows, this variable 
> doesn't need to be set because you can set the current directory from the 
> icon.  Also, it seems pointless to provide Motif and XView versions.  The 
