Subject: Re: Calchart continuity
To: gmeeker@volga.EECS.Berkeley.EDU (Garrick Meeker)
Date: Fri, 5 Jul 1996 22:59:36 -0500 (CDT)
In-Reply-To: <Pine.ULT.3.91.960705175227.468A-100000@volga.EECS.Berkeley.EDU> from "Garrick Meeker" at Jul 5, 96 06:20:05 pm
