Date: Tue, 9 Jul 1996 20:45:00 -0500 (CDT)
In-Reply-To: <Pine.ULT.3.91.960708115217.7521A-100000@volga.EECS.Berkeley.EDU> from "Garrick Meeker" at Jul 8, 96 12:01:15 pm
