Subject: Re: CalChart lasso
To: gmeeker@volga.EECS.Berkeley.EDU (Garrick Meeker)
Date: Thu, 11 Jul 1996 11:19:31 -0500 (CDT)
In-Reply-To: <Pine.ULT.3.91.960709222821.27249A@volga.EECS.Berkeley.EDU> from "Garrick Meeker" at Jul 9, 96 10:41:46 pm
