Received: (from dci@localhost) by daisy.uchicago.edu (8.7.5/8.7.5) id NAA19259 for gmeeker@kerner.com; Mon, 14 Oct 1996 13:28:07 -0500 (CDT)
From: Dan Isaksen <dci@math.uchicago.edu>
Message-Id: <199610141828.NAA19259@daisy.uchicago.edu>
Subject: Re: Smart move
To: gmeeker (Garrick Meeker)
Date: Mon, 14 Oct 1996 13:28:06 -0500 (CDT)
In-Reply-To: <Pine.SUN.3.91.961014103803.22091E-100000@c3p0> from "Garrick Meeker" at Oct 14, 96 11:08:33 am
