From: Dan Isaksen <dci@math.uchicago.edu>
Message-Id: <199708201733.MAA17347@daisy.uchicago.edu>
Subject: Re: calchart continuity
To: gmeeker@kerner.com (Garrick Meeker)
Date: Wed, 20 Aug 1997 12:33:23 -0500 (CDT)
In-Reply-To: <Pine.SOL.3.91.970819181537.8834I-100000@cantina> from "Garrick Meeker" at Aug 19, 97 06:35:15 pm
