Subject: Re: bug report for 10/15/97 version
To: gmeeker@kerner.com (Garrick Meeker)
Date: Sun, 19 Oct 1997 14:37:57 -0500 (CDT)
In-Reply-To: <Pine.SGI.3.96.971017190743.8030A-100000@sear> from "Garrick Meeker" at Oct 17, 97 07:19:35 pm
