> meant that COUNTERMARCH came up second (after BLAM).  That was a mistake. 
> COUNTERMARCH is certainly the most complicated procedure; I'll save it for
> last.

Okay, you should probably save your test case though.  Then you can go
back and make sure I never break anything.

