I've put out a new version of calchart.  It has the stuff I already
mentioned (SP, GV, better error reporting, etc), DOF is working,
continuity is case insensitive, fountain can take step size arguments,
march can take a direction to face, and some colors have changed.  Oh, and
the default zoom can be configured in the config file.  It probably still
doesn't deal with negative beats correctly in all cases.  I only briefly
test this stuff, so let me know how it goes.  I've updated the manual to
reflect the new additions (but not the other changes you mentioned).  So
get the manual to see the new syntax for march and fountain.

