I've finally gone through your old messages and compiled a list for me to
work on over break.  I'm leaving tomorrow night, so let me know soon if I
missed anything.  I'll put the ones I don't get to in the manual.  I'll
try to keep it up-to-date so you can remember what I'm working on.

